# Default Verible Lint Rules for TB Evaluation Framework
# See: https://chipsalliance.github.io/verible/verilog_lint.html

# Naming conventions
-explicit-parameter-storage-type
-line-length=length:120
-no-tabs
-no-trailing-spaces

# Module structure
-module-filename
-posix-eof

# Style
-forbid-consecutive-null-statements
-forbid-line-continuations

# Disabled rules (too strict for typical TB code)
# -always-comb
# -always-ff-non-blocking
